{"title_page": "Ansolet Rossouw", "text_new": "{{notability|1=biography|date= May 2019}}\n{{Infobox model\n| name          = Ansolet Rossouw\n| image         =\n| image_size    = \n| caption       = \n| birth_name    = \n| birth_date    = {{Birth date and age|1999|10|23|df=yes}}\n| birth_place   = [[Jagersfontein]], [[Free State (province)|Free State]], [[South Africa]]\n| death_date    =\n| death_place   =\n| nationality   = [[South Africa]]n\n| height        = {{height|m=1.75}} \n| hair_color    = Light brown\n| eye_color     = Blue-green\n| agency       = {{Plainlist| \n* [[The Society Management]] (New York)\n* [[Elite Model Management]] (worldwide)\n* Why Not Model Management (Milan)\n* PMA (Hamburg)\n* FANJAM Model Management (Cape Town) <ref>{{Cite web | url=https://models.com/models/ansolet-rossouw | title=Ansolet Rossouw - Model}}</ref> }}\n}}\n\n'''Ansolet Rossouw''' (born 23 October 1999) is a [[South Africa|South African]] fashion model.\n\n== Early life ==\nRossouw was born in the [[Free State (province)|Free State]] to a [[boer]] family.<!--Note:Based on reports, it seems she was born in Jagersfontein but raised in Bloemfontein. I\u2019m honestly not sure--> She was interested in becoming a teacher.<ref name=CRFB>{{cite web|url=https://www.crfashionbook.com/fashion/a20630864/now-casting-ansolet-rossouw/|title=NOW CASTING: ANSOLET ROSSOUW|work=CR Fashion Book}}</ref>\n\n== Career ==\nRossouw was discovered on [[Instagram]] by a FANJAM Model Management agent.<ref name=\"w24\">{{cite web|url=https://www.w24.co.za/Style/Fashion/Style/exclusive-young-model-from-bloemfontein-might-be-the-next-big-thing-20180315|title=EXCLUSIVE: Young model from Bloem might be the next big thing|work=w24}}</ref> She has walked for brands such as [[Dolce & Gabbana]], [[Chanel]], [[Elie Saab]], [[Fendi]], [[Miu Miu]], [[Jil Sander]], [[Valentino (fashion house)|Valentino]], [[Emilio Pucci]], [[Maison Margiela]], [[Off-White]], [[Max Mara]], [[Yves Saint Laurent (brand)|Saint Laurent]], [[Rodarte]], and [[Missoni]].<ref name=\"w24\"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://fashionista.com/2018/03/new-top-fashion-models-faces-fall-2018|title=18 NEW TOP MODELS WHO HAD THE BIGGEST FALL 2018 BREAKOUT SEASONS|work=Fashionista}}</ref><ref name=MarieClaire>{{cite web|url=http://www.marieclaire.co.za/fashion/12-models-you-should-know|title=The 12 Most Sought-After Models You Should Know About|work=[[Marie Claire (magazine)|Marie Claire]] South Africa}}</ref>\n\nRossouw is one of the highest paid models in South Africa.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.iol.co.za/business-report/economy/beautiful-and-rich-a-list-of-the-top-earning-models-in-sa-15231454|title=BEAUTIFUL AND RICH: A list of the top earning models in SA|work=[[Independent Online (South Africa)|IOL]]}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n<!-- Inline citations added to your article will automatically display here. See https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/WP:REFB for instructions on how to add citations. -->\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Rossouw, Ansolet}}\n[[Category:1999 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:South African female models]]\n[[Category:People from Bloemfontein]]\n[[Category:The Society Management models]]\n", "text_old": "{{notability|1=biography|date= May 2019}}\n{{Infobox model\n| name          = Ansolet Rossouw\n| image         =\n| image_size    = \n| caption       = \n| birth_name    = \n| birth_date    = {{Birth date and age|1999|10|23|df=yes}}\n| birth_place   = [[Jagersfontein]], [[Free State (province)|Free State]], [[South Africa]]\n| death_date    =\n| death_place   =\n| nationality   = [[South Africa]]n\n| height        = {{height|m=1.75}} \n| hair_color    = Light brown\n| eye_color     = Blue-green\n| agency       = {{Plainlist| \n* [[The Society Management]] (New York)\n* [[Elite Model Management]] (worldwide)\n* Why Not Model Management (Milan)\n* PMA (Hamburg)\n* FANJAM Model Management (Cape Town) <ref>{{Cite web | url=https://models.com/models/ansolet-rossouw | title=Ansolet Rossouw - Model}}</ref> }}\n}}\n\n'''Ansolet Rossouw''' (born 23 October 1999) is a South African fashion model.\n\n== Early life ==\nRossouw was born in the [[Free State (province)|Free State]] to a [[boer]] family.<!--Note:Based on reports, it seems she was born in Jagersfontein but raised in Bloemfontein. I\u2019m honestly not sure--> She was interested in becoming a teacher.<ref name=CRFB>{{cite web|url=https://www.crfashionbook.com/fashion/a20630864/now-casting-ansolet-rossouw/|title=NOW CASTING: ANSOLET ROSSOUW|work=CR Fashion Book}}</ref>\n\n== Career ==\nRossouw was discovered on [[Instagram]] by a FANJAM Model Management agent.<ref name=\"w24\">{{cite web|url=https://www.w24.co.za/Style/Fashion/Style/exclusive-young-model-from-bloemfontein-might-be-the-next-big-thing-20180315|title=EXCLUSIVE: Young model from Bloem might be the next big thing|work=w24}}</ref> She has walked for brands such as [[Dolce & Gabbana]], [[Chanel]], [[Elie Saab]], [[Fendi]], [[Miu Miu]], [[Jil Sander]], [[Valentino (fashion house)|Valentino]], [[Emilio Pucci]], [[Maison Margiela]], [[Off-White]], [[Max Mara]], [[Yves Saint Laurent (brand)|Saint Laurent]], [[Rodarte]], and [[Missoni]].<ref name=\"w24\"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://fashionista.com/2018/03/new-top-fashion-models-faces-fall-2018|title=18 NEW TOP MODELS WHO HAD THE BIGGEST FALL 2018 BREAKOUT SEASONS|work=Fashionista}}</ref><ref name=MarieClaire>{{cite web|url=http://www.marieclaire.co.za/fashion/12-models-you-should-know|title=The 12 Most Sought-After Models You Should Know About|work=[[Marie Claire (magazine)|Marie Claire]] South Africa}}</ref>\n\nRossouw is one of the highest paid models in South Africa.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.iol.co.za/business-report/economy/beautiful-and-rich-a-list-of-the-top-earning-models-in-sa-15231454|title=BEAUTIFUL AND RICH: A list of the top earning models in SA|work=[[Independent Online (South Africa)|IOL]]}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n<!-- Inline citations added to your article 